{
  "text": "That was this seems to be connected with the concept of the birds being messengers in the tarot. And this is a demonstration of this concept in the Tureau, and I was wondering about the mechanics, you might say, of this type of a message. I assumed the Hulk was a messenger, and I assume that as I thought of the possible meaning of this with respect to our activities, I was in the uh in a state of free will getting a message through the appearance of this very unusual bird, unusual I say it, in that it came so close. I would be very interested to know the origin of the message. Of course, the origin is the one creator. But I mean the mechanics of this are very mystifying to me.",
